%section
	%h1.center-text Our Community
	- @users.each do |user|
		-if user.profile
			-if user.profile.avatar			
				%div.comment
					%div.comment-image
						= link_to user do 
							= image_tag user.profile.avatar.url(:thumb), class: 'user-index-avatar'
					%div.comment-content
						= link_to user do 
							%h1
								= user.profile.first_name
								= user.profile.last_name
						-if user.plan_id == 2
							%span PRO
				%div.border-bottom
